Oh and in ShopAssistant, you can do this for getting the value:
[code=java]
	public int getItemShopValue(int itemId) {
		if (itemId < 0)
			return 0;
		return ItemDefinitions.getDefinitions()[itemId].getShopPrice();
	}[/code]

